sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Server

    Note over Client: State: Idle
    Note over Server: State: Idle

    Client->>Server: ClientHello (supported ciphers, random)
    Note over Client: State: ClientHelloSent

    Server->>Client: ServerHello (chosen cipher, random)
    Server->>Client: Certificate (server public key)
    Server->>Client: ServerHelloDone
    Note over Server: State: ServerHelloDone

    Client->>Server: ClientKeyExchange (encrypted pre-master secret)
    Client->>Server: ChangeCipherSpec
    Client->>Server: Finished (client verify data)
    Note over Client: State: KeyExchangeSent

    Server->>Client: ChangeCipherSpec
    Server->>Client: Finished (server verify data)
    Note over Server: State: Established

    Note over Client: State: Established
    Note over Client,Server: TLS Session Active — encrypted communication begins

